WEBVTT

00:08:29.583 --> 00:08:33.476
which is so often associated with loss,

00:08:33.500 --> 00:08:36.250
can become generative.

00:08:37.458 --> 00:08:41.726
But so many settings of care

00:08:41.750 --> 00:08:44.768
offer bingo

00:08:44.792 --> 00:08:46.708
and balloon toss.

00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:52.542
Activities are passive
and entertainment-oriented.

00:08:53.083 --> 00:08:57.958
Elders sit and watch and applaud,

00:08:59.750 --> 00:09:02.792
really just distracted
until the next meal.